{
  "chapter": 55,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙设下假计划诱骗赵雅，声称会先送赵雅、赵倩和小盘出城，再劫持朱姬母子，实则以此套取赵穆方面的情报。农牧节当日，乌卓在夫人府后门截获赵雅，将其捆绑，赵倩则改装为男儿身。项少龙率滕翼、荆俊等人伏击质子府车队，全歼护送赵兵，却发现马车中只有齐国特使齐雨而非朱姬。项少龙胁迫齐雨配合，返回质子府。郭开闻讯赶来，亦被制服。朱姬假扮郭开，在肖月潭协助下成功瞒过守门兵头陈佳，众人乘马车无惊无险离开质子府。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "事情进行得如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "还算顺利，你那处有什么新的消息，赵穆有没有收到风声？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "王兄和赵穆的精神都摆在和燕人的战争上，暂时无暇顾及其他事情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "倒是晶王后催促你快点动手，着我告诉你王兄因你与李牧合谋上书一事非常不满，极有可能在农牧节后对付你和乌家。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你们与吕不韦他们联络上了吗？若没有秦人的接应，怎把朱姬母子送回咸阳去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "早联络上了，他们派图先率人来接应，但仍不信任我们，只说我们若能把朱姬母子偷出城外，便到城西的马股山与他们会合。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "现在只剩下两天时间，出城的秘道弄好了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "一切预备妥当。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "对我来说，你和倩儿比朱姬母子更重要，所以我决定先把你、倩儿和小盘三人送往城外，才发动对你王兄赴牧场车队和质子府的突袭，否则宁愿取消整个计划。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们真的是那么重要吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "失去你们，我还有什么乐趣，依照往例，你王兄的车队将于大后天辰时中离城，我会早少许于卯时末在后门处等你们，若诸事妥当，立即派人先送你们到城西，待我劫到朱姬母子后，再来与你们会合，一起由秘道离城。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "谁负责城外的伏击呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "当然由乌卓负责，车队经过长草原时，我们的人会藏在预先挖好的箭坑内，在他们毫无防范下，只是弩弓劲箭，便教他们应付不了，这计划可说万无一失。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好吧！到时我会和三公主、小盘溜出来与你会合。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "难怪小盘这些天来行为古怪，不时自言自语，累得我还以为他念母过度，失了常性，又不敢告诉你，怕分你的心神。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "除你和廷芳外，便没有人知悉他真正的身份，所以无论在任何情况下，你绝不可揭破此事。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我明白！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "小孩胆子较小，我想先把小盘带走，雅儿有什么意见？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "有什么心事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家太高兴哩！故如此失态！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "去找小盘吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他仍未习惯自己的真正身份，让我带他去让廷芳照顾，待他见到王后再说吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人你好！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "少龙呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "你这又蠢又贱的荡货，竟敢出卖我们项爷，真是不知自量。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夫人会否这么轻易溜出来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "一定可以！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你是何人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "齐雨",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大爷饶命，我是齐国派来的特使，与你们无冤无仇。",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qi_yu",
      "text": "你要左眼还是右眼？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "齐雨",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "饶命啊！你要我干什么我便干什么。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qi_yu",
      "text": "我只要你回质子府去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "兵卫",
      "listener": "char_qi_yu",
      "text": "齐爷回来何事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "齐雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我遗下重要文件，须到夫人处取回来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "兵卫",
      "listener": "char_qi_yu",
      "text": "郭大夫有命，任何人不得进入质子府。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "齐雨",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这文件与贵国大王有关，非常重要，万事有我担当，快放行！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_qi_yu",
      "text": "宅内还有多少人？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qi_yu",
      "speaker_name": "齐雨",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还有五个婢女，其中两人陪着朱姬。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_qi_yu",
      "text": "使节大人为何去而复返，昨夜尚未尽兴吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_kai",
      "speaker_name": "郭开",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你们绝逃不出去的！",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_guo_kai",
      "text": "谁要逃出去？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "押他们上去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "政儿呢？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "幸不辱命！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "他……他长得像不像大王？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "像极了，体质则像夫人那么好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "给我宰了他！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "留下他的命比杀他更令他受罪。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你是个好心肠的人！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_qi_yu",
      "text": "若非你是由齐国来的贵宾，本官必把你当廷杖责。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "本官要和使节大人往外一趟，你们小心把守门户。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 329
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chen_jia",
      "speaker_name": "兵头陈佳",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "大人！这处怎能没有你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我自有主张，哪轮到你陈佳来管我，快开门！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 55,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 335
    }
  ],
